Project Title: Grafana AWS CloudWatch Integration

Description:

  This repository contains the code and configuration files for setting up Grafana
 in an EC2 instance and connecting it to AWS CloudWatch for monitoring and visualization 
 of metrics. The project is part of a learning exercise to gain proficiency in Terraform
  and Ansible while exploring Grafana's capabilities.

  day 1 - established the foundational infrastructure for the project using Terraform.
   This included creating a Virtual Private Cloud (VPC), a public subnet, and launching an EC2
    instance. Ensured secure access via SSH and Grafana ports while following best practices
     for handling sensitive data and maintaining clear documentation.